lead_paragraph: Jordan Morris scored in the 56th minute on a pass from Nelson Haedo Valdez as the visiting Seattle Sounders beat the Colorado Rapids 1-0 on Sunday to advance to their first MLS Cup final.

headline.print_headline: Sounders Beat Rapids to Reach Their First MLS Cup Final
